 class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.obj₂\">obj₂</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₂</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.obj₂\">obj₂</a></span>),\n          <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₁\">mor₁</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₂</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₁\">mor₁</a></span></span> →\n            <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.obj₃\">obj₃</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₂</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.obj₃\">obj₃</a></span>),\n              <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₂\">mor₂</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">c</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₂</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₂\">mor₂</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a>                 <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₃\">mor₃</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Shift/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.shiftFunctor\">shiftFunctor</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Functor/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Functor.map\">map</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">c</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T₂</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.Triangle.mor₃\">mor₃</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated\">Pretriangulated</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.mk","kind":"ctor","line":65,"name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.lean#L65-L65"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">Pretriangulated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v, u}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/ZeroObjects.html#CategoryTheory.Limits.HasZeroObject\">Limits.HasZeroObject</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Shift/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.HasShift\">HasShift</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">ℤ</a></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Preadditive/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Preadditive\">Preadditive</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">ℤ</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Shift/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.shiftFunctor\">shiftFunctor</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Preadditive/AdditiveFunctor.html#CategoryTheory.Functor.Additive\">Additive</a></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max u v)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A preadditive category `C` with an additive shift, and a class of \"distinguished triangles\"\nrelative to that shift is called pretriangulated if the following hold:\n* Any triangle that is isomorphic to a distinguished triangle is also distinguished.\n* Any triangle of the form `(X,X,0,id,0,0)` is distinguished.\n* For any morphism `f : X ⟶ Y` there exists a distinguished triangle of the form `(X,Y,Z,f,g,h)`.\n* The triangle `(X,Y,Z,f,g,h)` is distinguished if and only if `(Y,Z,X⟦1⟧,g,h,-f⟦1⟧)` is.\n* Given a diagram:\n  ```\n        f       g       h\n    X  ───> Y  ───> Z  ───> X⟦1⟧\n    │       │                │\n    │a      │b               │a⟦1⟧'\n    V       V                V\n    X' ───> Y' ───> Z' ───> X'⟦1⟧\n        f'      g'      h'\n  ```\n  where the left square commutes, and whose rows are distinguished triangles,\n  there exists a morphism `c : Z ⟶ Z'` such that `(a,b,c)` is a triangle morphism.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.html#CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated","kind":"class","line":45,"name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Triangulated/Pretriangulated.lean#L45-L85"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.Homology.ShortComplex.Basic","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Limits.Constructions.FiniteProductsOfBinaryProducts","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Triangulated.TriangleShift"],"instances":[{"className":"CategoryTheory.SplitEpiCategory","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instSplitEpiCategory","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.SplitMonoCategory","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instSplitMonoCategory","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasBinaryBiproducts","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instHasBinaryBiproducts","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasFiniteProducts","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instHasFiniteProducts","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasFiniteCoproducts","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instHasFiniteCoproducts","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasFiniteBiproducts","name":"CategoryTheory.Pretriangulated.instHasFiniteBiproducts","typeNames":[]}],"name":"Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Triangulated.Pretriangulated"}